## Install Shared Folder at VMware
https://linuxhint.com/mount_vmware_shares_command_line_linux_vm/

## Generate SSH Key
```bash
ssh-keygen -t rsa
```

## Istall VSCode
https://computingforgeeks.com/how-to-install-visual-studio-code-on-kali-linux/

## Install Ruby as normal user + Jekyll
sudo apt-get install ruby-full build-essential zlib1g-dev

echo '# Install Ruby Gems to ~/gems' >> ~/.bashrc
echo 'export GEM_HOME="$HOME/gems"' >> ~/.bashrc
echo 'export PATH="$HOME/gems/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

gem install jekyll bundler

## BurpSuite embed browser did not work
sudo find .BurpSuite -name chrome-sandbox -exec chown root:root {} \; -exec chmod 4755 {} \;

## Unzip
$ sudo gzip -d rockyou.txt.gz 
